{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dissimilar blends together semi-open exploration, a narrative laced with mysteries, and an engaging turn-based battle system.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904360/extras/dissimilar_main_s.gif?t=1729086968\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Amelia expected her evening to be perfectly ordinary. What she did not expect was for her best friend to hack her automated car and bring her against her will to the Haven, the ancient castle her family used to holiday in when she was a child.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As Amelia seeks to understand why she was kidnapped, she finds herself forced to participate in a mysterious game; a game of unknown rules and goals, which will lead her to walk the Haven's storied halls and uncover secrets long buried by her family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904360/extras/dissimilar_exploration_s.gif?t=1729086968\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Haven's fully hand-drawn grounds are yours to explore freely, but it will be no simple task: your observation skills, your sense of curiosity and an organised approach will be your best friends as you attempt to unearth the mysteries hiding in this expansive, semi-open domain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many trials await you in this ancient castle, and a keen sense of adventure just might lead you to areas you were never meant to explore...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904360/extras/dissimilar_battle_s.gif?t=1729086968\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Organise your team and plan your strategy around enemy actions in tactical turn-based battles where every action you take - or don't \u2013 matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Despite this, your adventure will not meet a premature end: instead of losing you progress, every defeat is an opportunity for you to learn more about your enemies and adjust your strategies, using the many Fighters and unique skills in your arsenal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904360/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729086968","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904360/page.bg.jpg?t=1729086968","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904360/4a1c2e50717b7c37a0960194ec82f63c37a9c914/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729086968","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904360/4a1c2e50717b7c37a0960194ec82f63c37a9c914/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729086968","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2904480,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dissimilar blends together semi-open exploration, a narrative laced with mysteries, and an engaging turn-based battle system.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904360/extras/dissimilar_main_s.gif?t=1729086968\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Amelia expected her evening to be perfectly ordinary. What she did not expect w